{
  "texts": [
    "DiscussionWe successfully developed a multimodal large language model capable of accurately detecting major pathological findings in CXRs and generating free-text radiologic reports.",
    "Our model exhibited relatively good performance compared to other publicly available general-purpose multimodal LLMs, such as GPT-4-vision and Gemini-Pro-Vision.",
    "We also explored the potential of multimodal LLMs for autonomous or semi-autonomous reporting in chest radiography.",
    "However, there are some limitations to our study.",
    "First, the evaluation method we employed has inherent limitations."
  ]
}